パッケージ manhattan.dsminformation

  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    BPinfo
    Information file for computation of back propagation.
    DSMheader
    Header part of a file for DSM.
    FPinfo
    Information file for computation of forward propagation.
    InformationFileMaker
    This class makes information files for
    SHBP SHFP PSVBP PSVFP TODO information of eliminated stations and events
    InformationFileReader
    Reader for files which contains c # !
    PolynomialStructure
    Structure of the Earth for DSM input
    Every depth is written in radius.
    SshDSMinfo
    Information file for SSHPSV and SSHSH
    SshDSMInformationFileMaker
    Information file for SSHSH
    SyntheticDSMInfo
    Information file for TIPSV and TISH
    SyntheticDSMInformationFileMaker
    作業フォルダ下のイベント群に対してDSM(tipsv, tish)のinformation fileを作る
